sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(230, 126, 34) Customer
        participant Cust as Customer
    end
    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker
        participant Portal as Yves Returns Portal
        participant Return as Return Management
        participant OMS as OMS (return sub-process)
        participant DB as MariaDB
    end
    box rgb(39, 174, 96) Carriers
        participant Carrier as DHL / DPD / GLS
    end

    Cust->>Portal: Open returns portal, select order/items
    Portal->>Return: Create return (items in Shipped/Delivered, within Return Policy window)
    Return->>DB: Persist return + return items
    Return->>OMS: Start return OMS sub-process
    Note over OMS: Return items move through their own OMS states
    OMS->>OMS: onEnter transition -> ReturnLabelCommand
    OMS->>Carrier: Request return label [REST]
    Carrier-->>OMS: Return label (PDF/URL)
    OMS->>DB: Store carrier label reference on return
    Portal-->>Cust: Show return confirmation + downloadable label
    Note over Carrier: Carrier-label generation is a CUSTOM OMS command<br/>(not an OOTB packaged capability)
